  <outcomes>
    <primaryOutcome>
      <outcome>Assign molecular scores (probability) of T cell mediated rejection, antibody mediated rejection in heart transplant biopsies, in a reference set of 200 biopsies - Create molecular classifier that predicts antibody mediated and T cell mediated rejection</outcome>
      <timepoint>2 years</timepoint>
    </primaryOutcome>
    <secondaryOutcome>
      <outcome>Assign in real time (three working days upon biopsy receipt) molecular scores (probability) of T cell mediated rejection and antibody mediated rejection. - The molecular phenotype of a newly acquired sample predicts the histologic and clinical features of this sample when compared to the reference set.</outcome>
      <timepoint>1 year</timepoint>
    </secondaryOutcome>
  </outcomes>
